{
  "texts": [
    "It allows more people to participate in the development and use of AI and promotes inclusion in the AI era.",
    "Using social robots as learning companions has been proven to help students understand AI principles (Su & Zhong, 2022: 1).",
    "Participating students could propose authentic scenarios, apply their new knowledge of AI, and devise meaningful AI-based solutions in digital stories (Mertala et al., 2022; Ng et al., 2022).",
    "Therefore, AI literacy education and training must prepare society to face a future increasingly connected to AI technology (Dai et al., 2023: 84).",
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) has significantly changed the landscape of language education."
  ]
}